            "block_description": "Everything you need to know about lab grown diamonds.",
            "faq_question_1": "What are lab grown diamonds?",
            "faq_answer_1": "<p>Lab grown diamonds are real diamonds created in controlled laboratory environments. They have the same physical, chemical, and optical properties as natural diamonds, offering identical brilliance and durability.</p>",
