            "faq_question_3": "How are lab grown diamonds different from natural diamonds?",
            "faq_answer_3": "<p>The main difference is how they are formed. Natural diamonds form over billions of years underground, while lab grown diamonds are created using advanced technology. Visually and structurally, they are the same.</p>",
            "faq_question_4": "Are lab grown diamonds certified?",
            "faq_answer_4": "<p>Yes. Lab grown diamonds are certified by internationally recognised gemological institutes such as IGI and SGL. Certification ensures quality, authenticity, and transparency in grading.</p>",
